1.- Intro to Vuex
Every component has direct access to this global state
When one componene update the state, other component actually.

data = state
method = actions
computer = getters

the diferents is, the store also has mutations:
Mutations are used to commit and track state changes
Las mutaciones se utilizan para confirmar y realizar un seguimiento de los cambios de estado.

Actions -> Mutations -> state

Vuex provides
 - Single source of truth
 - Common library of actions, mutations, getters

Link: https://vuex.vuejs.org/#what-is-a-state-management-pattern

